# User Management API Test File
# Use with REST Client extension in VS Code

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### Register User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Register Another User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Smith",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "pass"
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Verify Email (replace :id with actual user ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/verify/1

### Get All Users (requires authentication - add Bearer token)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Block Users (bulk operation)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/block
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "userIds": [1, 2]
}

### Unblock Users (bulk operation)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/unblock
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "userIds": [1, 2]
}

### Delete Users (bulk operation)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/delete
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "userIds": [2]
}

### Delete Unverified Users
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/users/unverified
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE